title: Adam Ferrara: Long Island Kid
description:
Kippy and Foley are back with a hot one featuring Adam Ferrara! They talk Adam growing up in Long Island, being Italian, and starting comedy in the 90s in NYC. Its a fun one! Thanks for listening. Love youse guys.
